---
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding border-t border-neutral-800/50">
  <div class="container-max">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="reveal-left">
        <p class="text-brand-500 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">About</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Built by practitioners,<br />
          <span class="text-slate-400">not project managers.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Most Salesforce projects fail not because of the technology — but because the implementation
            doesn't reflect how the business actually works. We built CipherCloud Studio around fixing that.
          </p>
          <p>
            With 11+ years of hands-on delivery across Sales Cloud, Service Cloud, Loyalty Cloud,
            Field Service Lightning, Experience Cloud, and complex Salesforce integrations — we know
            what good implementation looks like, and what it costs when it goes wrong.
            Three active certifications back the work.
          </p>
          <p>
            We've worked inside the kinds of orgs we now help build — enterprise teams, regulated
            industries, high-growth SMBs. That experience shapes how we engage: directly with owners
            and teams, no account managers, no bloated timelines. You get people who ask the right
            questions before touching the keyboard.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-block mt-8 bg-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Start a project
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {[
          { label: 'Focus', value: 'Outcomes over deliverables' },
          { label: 'Style', value: 'Direct. No jargon.' },
          { label: 'Clients', value: 'SMBs & growing teams' },
          { label: 'Approach', value: 'Config-first, code when needed' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">{item.label}</p>
            <p class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">{item.value}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
